headline: 3 Internet Stocks with Exciting Potential
summary: Whether it be online shopping or social media, secular forces are propelling consumer internet businesses forward. These themes have enabled rapid growth for the industry, which has posted a 8.9% gain over the past six months. This was a good place to be as the S&P 500 shed 1.1% of its value.

headline: Agoda Offers Free Tickets for Japanese Fans to See NCT WISH, THE BOYZ, n.SSign and More at Seoul Spring Festa
